task.summary: how to inject value in spring
In prototype scope, you will have a new instance for each getBean() method called.
Create a concrete List collection class (ArrayList and LinkedList), and inject it into bean property.
Create a concrete Set collection class (HashSet and TreeSet), and inject it into bean property.
I have instantiated a HashMap and injected it into Customer’s map property at runtime.
Spring is accepting date variable, here’s a tip to use CustomDateEditor to work around it.
